Winner of the 2022 Norma Patton-Lowin Makeup Award at the Hollywood beauty awards, Alexx continues to push the boundaries of color and dimension with every single look he creates. Working with Lizzo, Adut Akech, Mariah Carey, Ming Lee Simmons, JoJo, and Tinashe have been some of his career highlights. His work has graced the covers of Vogue, Essence, Variety, L’Officiel, Variety, Elle, Rolling Stone, Time Magazine, Marie Claire, Sports Illustrated, and many more.
